2026-05-15T22:49:22.6618535Z 13    <!--
2026-05-15T22:49:22.6619122Z 14        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-15T22:49:22.6619994Z 15        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
2026-05-15T22:49:22.6621169Z 16        Settings → Notifications. Android 14+ restricts this to apps whose
2026-05-15T22:49:22.6622085Z 17        core function is alarms/calendar/communication; for other apps the
2026-05-15T22:49:22.6623027Z 18        system downgrades it to a heads-up notification, which is fine —
2026-05-15T22:49:22.6623784Z 19        we only request it when the toggle is on.
2026-05-15T22:49:22.6624583Z 20    -->
2026-05-15T22:49:22.6625406Z 21    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.USE_FULL_SCREEN_INTENT" />
2026-05-15T22:49:22.6626407Z 21-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml:16:5-81
2026-05-15T22:49:22.6627423Z 21-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml:16:22-78
2026-05-15T22:49:22.6628170Z 22    <!--
2026-05-15T22:49:22.6628819Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-15T22:49:22.6629555Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-05-15T22:49:22.6630229Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-15T22:49:22.6631069Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-15T22:49:22.6631893Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-15T22:49:22.6632707Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-15T22:49:22.6633522Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-15T22:49:22.6634361Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-15T22:49:22.6635363Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-15T22:49:22.6636126Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-15T22:49:22.6636753Z 33    -->
2026-05-15T22:49:22.6637390Z 34    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM" />
2026-05-15T22:49:22.6638442Z 34-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml:29:5-79
2026-05-15T22:49:22.6639515Z 34-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml:29:22-76
2026-05-15T22:49:22.6640721Z 35    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.USE_EXACT_ALARM" />
