2026-05-15T22:49:22.6676546Z 36-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml:31:22-78
2026-05-15T22:49:22.6677353Z 37    <!--
2026-05-15T22:49:22.6677934Z 38        Used on Samsung and other OEM devices that aggressively optimize
2026-05-15T22:49:22.6678805Z 39        battery usage. MainActivity shows a one-time dialog that opens
