2026-05-15T22:49:22.7371860Z 250        <!--
2026-05-15T22:49:22.7372468Z 251            Same hardening for Glance's InvisibleActionTrampolineActivity.
2026-05-15T22:49:22.7373376Z 252            The library entry is singleInstance with its own taskAffinity
2026-05-15T22:49:22.7374225Z 253            but omits excludeFromRecents (unlike its sibling
2026-05-15T22:49:22.7405466Z 254            ActionTrampolineActivity which already has it). When the
2026-05-15T22:49:22.7406394Z 255            process dies before the trampoline finishes, the system can
2026-05-15T22:49:22.7407247Z 256            restore the task from Recents and replay onCreate with a
2026-05-15T22:49:22.7408401Z 257            stale Intent whose ACTION_INTENT extra is missing — which
2026-05-15T22:49:22.7409255Z 258            triggers an IllegalArgumentException ("List adapter activity
2026-05-15T22:49:22.7410140Z 259            trampoline invoked without specifying target intent"). Adding
2026-05-15T22:49:22.7411281Z 260            excludeFromRecents removes the Recents restoration vector,
2026-05-15T22:49:22.7412157Z 261            matching what Glance already does for ActionTrampolineActivity.
